  Stable on x86; bug #119853

  22 Jan 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> audacious-0.1.2.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64. Bug #119853.

  12 Dec 2005; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  audacious-0.1.2.ebuild:
  Rekeyworded ~sparc after masking modplug wrt #115228

*audacious-0.1.2 (11 Dec 2005)

  11 Dec 2005; <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +audacious-0.1.2.ebuild:
  Version bump. Lost ~sparc keyword over libmodplug.

*audacious-0.1.1 (27 Nov 2005)

  27 Nov 2005; <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +audacious-0.1.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. No longer reruns autotools, closes bug #112990.

  20 Nov 2005; <chainsaw@gentoo.org> audacious-0.1-r1.ebuild:
  Install libFLAC.m4, which is available separately. Closes bug #112990.

  14 Nov 2005; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  audacious-0.1-r1.ebuild:
  Keyworded ~sparc wrt #112452

  14 Nov 2005; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> audacious-0.1.ebuild:
  Marking audacious-0.1 ~ppc64 for bug request 112452

*audacious-0.1-r1 (01 Nov 2005)

